Responsibilities

  Responsible for daily mold change overs and setup inspection.
  Molds cavities efficiency are maintained at 95% or better
  Evaluates the possibilities of rectifying or simply molds for better changeability or moldability
  Exercises teamwork within toolmakers by assisting each other on daily change over upon completion of jobs
  Assists in mold setup and inspection before production
  Ensures all molds are in proper maintained and recorded as per the frequency of the mold cycle
  Ensure machines area are clean during mold setup
  Other duties as assigned by the Management

Requirements

  Candidate must possess at least a Professional Certificate/NITEC in Engineering or equivalent
  At least 3 years of working experience in Tool and Die making
